Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.66,0:01:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五十六話\N極限的勝負\N瞬天殺對抗天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.27,0:01:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有某種東西…跟剛才不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.94,0:02:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對…明顯的\N這不是平時的小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者生 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.45,0:02:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時保護我的是\N志志雄告訴我的真理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.49,0:02:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就差在一把短刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.09,0:02:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以正確的是志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.86,0:02:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有感情的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.47,0:02:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管行動再快\N還是可以讀出動向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.47,0:02:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.15,0:02:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.66,0:02:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼不殺我 你以為你贏了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.43,0:02:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的 那時候沒保護你的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.97,0:03:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管我再怎麼想\N都想不出頭緒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.18,0:03:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我瞭解一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.51,0:03:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在封閉起來的意識深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在深深後悔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.85,0:03:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.89,0:03:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不想傷害任何人的活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的一個感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果還來得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以現在重新開始呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄教給我的真理…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.62,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…弱者…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那麼該死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.83,0:04:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是殺了人 但
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本不想殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想殺人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.04,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 我在那場雨中笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是其實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(我是在哭泣)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎崩潰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.57,0:05:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的存在妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你交手 我就變得奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不管什麼是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那都不重要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一擊 我一定要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要出招了 你有覺悟了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是拔刀術姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.81,0:05:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右手稍微放低了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想用速度來決鬥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我唯一命名的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.02,0:06:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞬天殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.39,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是名符其實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.59,0:06:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可讓人瞬間死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你感覺不到痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.00,0:06:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以縮地術突擊\N再加上天劍的拔刀術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.03,0:06:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個連環絕招\N有效的話確實是瞬間致命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.04,0:06:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 以你混亂的心\N你現在能下那決心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.05,0:06:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此  你把一切都看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很從容嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.75,0:06:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 他哪裏從容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷經了與蒼紫的激烈戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.82,0:06:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還受到一個\N沒拿出全力的小鬼壓迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的從容是因為他\N只知道這戰鬥方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.00,0:06:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其擔心\N不如擔心自己吧 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你讀出我的動向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.91,0:07:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也來不及反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為瞬天殺太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.01,0:07:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.25,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收刀了 那是拔刀術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這緊要關頭使出的拔刀術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對是那招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.16,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流秘技   天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.34,0:07:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.17,0:07:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我隨時都是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.21,0:07:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的話 對方也不會當真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了 我會拋棄我的傲慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認真與你交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認真對抗認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.49,0:07:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙方都使出全力了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.46,0:07:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.67,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算贏了 還是找不出答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正正確的是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的瞬天殺   看你能否看透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.52,0:08:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失了 這就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縮地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙方一樣的快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 決勝負的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.30,0:08:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕招的破壞力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟新月村的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.24,0:09:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到完全反過來的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他居然能一本不殺的初衷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.82,0:09:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變強到這程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.99,0:09:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點…狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狡猾？小弟弟你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.03,0:09:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要把組合錯誤的積木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確組合起來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不一口氣整個打垮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沒辦法辦到的 由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.91,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來過去是我錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.05,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場決鬥讓我得到了答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.45,0:10:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確的人是緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.86,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.73,0:10:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獲勝的 也就是強者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.14,0:10:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強者 正確的是志志雄的理論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.37,0:10:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只要靠一兩次戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能得出真實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.84,0:10:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰還會過著錯誤的生活呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.01,0:10:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的人生不是那麼簡單的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真實的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.55,0:10:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必需在自己身上\N自己的生活中找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.16,0:10:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像你走過的那樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嚴格的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.85,0:10:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不輕易給人答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.88,0:11:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比志志雄更嚴格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像被整得很慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.99,0:11:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這地方打混什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.09,0:11:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊他們早就往前趕去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.60,0:11:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 那無所謂\N事情都照預計的順利進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基地中心部份的位置圖\N你是何時弄到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要收集這個國家的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.72,0:12:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是國家機構效率最高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.42,0:12:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我當\N警視廳的探子的理由之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.66,0:12:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來到這裏就不需要帶路人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.16,0:12:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分成兩路比較聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.13,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是…要把拔刀齊他們\N當成引開注意力的棄卒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多是那樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.54,0:12:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從幕末到現在\N與拔刀齊的決鬥還沒分出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.88,0:12:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果拔刀齊在這裏死掉\N你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時當然是活下來的人贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.22,0:12:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你派上了不少用場   托你的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.16,0:12:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人跟拔刀齊才沒有注意到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我就能像影子一樣行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.30,0:13:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前新撰組三號隊隊長   齊藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.77,0:13:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到幕末的京都\N會聚集這麼多強者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.14,0:13:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也有加入戰鬥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在眷念什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在比過去重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該戰鬥的時刻是 現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.79,0:13:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不知道要不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.46,0:13:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的啦 他看來生命無恙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我不是指肉體的傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.93,0:13:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的是他自己心理上的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.14,0:13:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我們能插嘴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.04,0:13:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只要想著如何前進就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.81,0:13:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要緊了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.36,0:13:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我差不多該向前進了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別擔心前面的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面那扇門的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.93,0:14:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是直接通往\N志志雄的房間的最短捷徑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.23,0:14:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請利用那個搶先緋村他們\N回去轉告志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.41,0:14:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我所看到的天翔龍閃的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天翔龍閃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真面目？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.85,0:14:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 那瞬間我看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.69,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左腳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀術的法則本來是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.24,0:14:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了不砍到自己的腳\N右足必定踏向前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.47,0:14:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是緋村他卻是踩左足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.18,0:14:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在不妨礙手的動作\N與腰的扭力的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.35,0:14:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在拔刀之前\N瞬間向前衝踩出的最後一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給予刀加速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使神速的拔刀術\N轉變成超神速的拔刀術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.03,0:15:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣 只有一步不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.16,0:15:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那一步是最難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.83,0:15:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在生與死的極限之間\N再向前踏出一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.71,0:15:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有一種拚命的\N或是死中求生存的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種負面的心境的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.38,0:15:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就絕對不可贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.05,0:15:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許志志雄大人的實力\N能打敗他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.69,0:15:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟 你是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.19,0:15:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天翔龍閃必需踏出左足才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.23,0:15:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以與其注意眼睛與手\N不如把注意擺在緋村的左腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.23,0:15:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論面臨什麼樣的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.00,0:15:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都能預先察知\N他何時會使出天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.34,0:15:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  我趕快去通知志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的 我還想拜託另一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.32,0:16:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.32,0:16:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前志志雄送我的短刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.93,0:16:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十年來  那是我最珍貴的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.66,0:16:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想把它還給志志雄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.43,0:16:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟 這麼說 你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.74,0:16:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救了差點被殺的我的是志志雄跟那把短刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是千真萬確的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.25,0:16:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想照緋村說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.25,0:16:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後自己一個人\N去找出真正的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.82,0:16:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告別了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.53,0:16:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對你而言 那可能是最好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.64,0:17:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄的事就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.81,0:17:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不必拜託我\N志志雄是天下無敵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不是那意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.09,0:17:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見 你多保重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.71,0:17:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了…志志雄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.62,0:17:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦…宗次郎把\N天翔龍閃的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.96,0:17:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當作告別的禮物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子能戰鬥的只有我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.47,0:18:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正沒有人會因為\N我的強大而跟隨我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.84,0:18:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來那傢伙還是一貫不殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.14,0:18:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬人拔刀齊並沒有覺醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.31,0:18:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這情況下他卻還有能力\N打倒宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為一個劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他決鬥 跟篡奪一個國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樣的令我熱血沸騰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.72,0:18:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我很不甘願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煉獄被燒燬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大半士兵被捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.93,0:18:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後連十本刀也瓦解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.00,0:18:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子掌握日本的計劃\N要延後十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.27,0:18:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心吧 我一個人就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是差個十年的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.71,0:18:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀 根本不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.55,0:18:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在西歐強國逐漸把\N弱國化成殖民地的現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓近代日本存活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.25,0:18:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至高無上力量之存在\N是絕對需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.19,0:18:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 志志雄這個絕對的強者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都是為了志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.56,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,需要的話 化成魔鬼也在所不惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.87,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒路了  這就是志志雄的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要看看他的嘴臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.81,0:19:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼慢 等得我累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.65,0:19:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…你是何時過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人在格鬥場等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.42,0:19:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 跟我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擺什麼架子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了 劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.63,0:19:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒問題…的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他很累的樣子哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是不用大腦\N誰叫他要連戰兩場呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.01,0:19:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是當然的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.58,0:19:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.81,0:19:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然這樣如何\N你們兩個可以臨陣脫逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.75,0:19:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你們答應\N今後不再妨礙志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.95,0:20:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就當作你們沒來到這裏\N中途回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.77,0:20:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你並不希望見到\N我與志志雄交手的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.01,0:20:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就我來看\N你是擔心志志雄有個萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.91,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虧我好心同情你們\N這兩個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.79,0:20:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如先前說的\N這是我與志志雄的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管發生什麼事都請你別插手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.78,0:20:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我不會坐視你死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥與小姐 他們都需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.35,0:21:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 不只如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.68,0:21:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的日本需要你這樣的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.19,0:21:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有那許多不認識的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.02,0:21:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算被罵為騙子 小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.56,0:21:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我若覺得情況不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.23,0:21:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會以右手最強的二重極\N介入決鬥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這扇門的另一邊是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.90,0:21:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄大人專用的格鬥場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大灼熱之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.90,0:21:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開的話你們就無路可逃了哦

